{
  "texts": [
    "The Evol platform offers a co-occurrence analysis module that shows connections between words from a contextual perspective.",
    "A screenshot of this function is shown in After these processes, the platform produces analysis results in two forms: word cloud diagrams for interactive visualization of statistical outcomes, and text retrieval results for the query.",
    "The number of co-occurrence words can be adjusted from 10 to 100.",
    "To optimize computational efficiency, pre-processed word segmentation data is used in this function, and precomputed word frequency results are employed for chapter and book levels.",
    "In addition to viewing the visualization results online, users can also download the complete co-occurrence statistics in XLSX format."
  ]
}